## Fix B.1 â€” orderGroups useMemo (full block replacement)

**Anchor:** `const orderGroups = useMemo` (1 hit ~3768)

âš ï¸ Read the actual block via `sed -n '3768,3825p'` before replacing â€” use exact whitespace from file as old_string. The block ends with `}, [visibleOrders, tableMap, isKitchen, activeRequests, openSessionByTableId]);`.

